## LONGEVITY GUIDE (For H2 #8)

**SELF-ADHESIVE STICKERS:**
- Without top coat: 1-3 days
- With top coat: 3-7 days
- With gel top coat: 5-10 days
- **Realistic expectation:** 5-7 days for daily wear

**WATER DECALS:**
- With regular top coat: 7-10 days
- With gel top coat: 10-14 days
- **Realistic expectation:** 10-14 days (longest-lasting type)
- **Why they last longer:** Ultra-thin, no raised edges to catch

**FULL NAIL WRAPS:**
- Semi-cured gel wraps: 7-10 days
- Regular vinyl wraps: 5-7 days
- **Realistic expectation:** 7-10 days with proper sealing

**FACTORS THAT REDUCE LONGEVITY:**
- Frequent hand washing (healthcare, food service)
- Hot water exposure (dishwashing without gloves)
- Swimming/prolonged water immersion
- Nail oil buildup (oily nail beds need more frequent cleaning)
- Manual labor (typing is fine, gardening/cleaning damages faster)

